Nah Skerang teamn-teman bisa monitori via web base ceph, silahkan ikuti perintah berikut. Installnya di node-00 selaku mgr 

sudo apt-get install ceph-mgr-dashboard

sudo ceph mgr module enable dashboard

sudo ceph dashboard ac-user-create admin 123456789 administrator

sudo ceph dashboard create-self-signed-cert

sudo ceph mgr services
